<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 09:12:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>欧洲股市持平，因为医疗保健行业的损失超过了矿业股</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-flat-losses-healthcare-outweigh-miners-2024-01-23/</link><description>欧洲股市周二开盘持平，医疗保健股的下跌部分抵消了矿业股的上涨，而市场焦点仍集中在欧洲央行将于本周晚些时候举行的政策会议上，以获取有关利率轨迹的信号。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 08:40:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-flat-losses-healthcare-outweigh-miners-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国希望联合国对人权的审查是建设性的、非政治化的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hopes-un-review-human-rights-constructive-non-politicised-2024-01-23/</link><description>中国外交部周二表示，希望联合国各方以“建设性”和“非政治化”的方式审查中国的人权记录。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 07:58:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hopes-un-review-human-rights-constructive-non-politicised-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国采取措施支撑股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/measures-china-has-taken-prop-up-its-stock-market-2024-01-23/</link><description>彭博新闻社报道称，中国当局正在考虑采取多项措施来提振股市，中国股市周二反弹。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 07:15:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/measures-china-has-taken-prop-up-its-stock-market-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>投资者对中国市场崩溃的看法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/what-investors-are-saying-about-chinas-market-meltdown-2024-01-23/</link><description>由于对世界第二大经济体的信心消失和外国资金外逃，中国和香港股市本周跌至多年低点，而数据显示经济增长缓慢，房地产市场萎靡不振。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 05:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/what-investors-are-saying-about-chinas-market-meltdown-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>德国总统和企业访问越南关注劳工协议和投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/german-president-businesses-visit-vietnam-eyeing-labour-deal-investment-2024-01-23/</link><description>一个由隧道机械、风力发电场和工业供应领域的顶级公司组成的德国商业代表团将于周二开始与总统弗兰克-瓦尔特·施泰因迈尔一起访问越南，德国政府正在推动其中国去风险战略。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 05:36:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/german-president-businesses-visit-vietnam-eyeing-labour-deal-investment-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡亚洲创世纪 (Asia Genesis) 在押注中国和日本失败后关闭对冲基金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/singapores-asia-genesis-closes-hedge-fund-after-losing-bets-china-japan-2024-01-23/</link><description>总部位于新加坡的亚洲创世纪资产管理公司(Asia Genesis Asset Management)正在清算其对冲基金，该基金在中国和日本押注失误后出现了“前所未有的大幅缩水”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 05:34:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/singapores-asia-genesis-closes-hedge-fund-after-losing-bets-china-japan-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本央行与通缩心态作斗争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-01-23/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 05:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国股票衍生品暴跌，韩国散户投资者遭受打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korean-retail-investors-hit-china-equity-derivatives-tumble-2024-01-23/</link><description>本月，香港主要股市指数下跌 11%，韩国散户投资者陷入困境，今年到期的约 15.4 万亿韩元（合 115 亿美元）的指数挂钩衍生品开始带来损失。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 05:18:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korean-retail-investors-hit-china-equity-derivatives-tumble-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉将于1月下旬开启Cyber​​truck中国行-外媒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-kick-off-cybertrucks-china-tour-late-jan-media-2024-01-23/</link><description>据澎湃新闻周二报道，特斯拉旗舰款 Cyber​​truck 皮卡全国巡展将于 1 月下旬拉开帷幕，8 辆卡车将在上海、首都北京等 8 个城市同时展出。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 03:40:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-kick-off-cybertrucks-china-tour-late-jan-media-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国监管机构从网站上删除了视频游戏规则草案；股价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-regulator-removes-draft-video-game-rules-website-shares-jump-2024-01-23/</link><description>路透社周二的调查显示，中国游戏监管机构已从其网站上删除了上个月提出的旨在限制鼓励玩视频游戏的支出和奖励的规定，此举提振了游戏公司的股价。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 03:15:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-regulator-removes-draft-video-game-rules-website-shares-jump-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国山体滑坡死亡人数上升至20人 救援人员仍在搜寻失踪者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/death-toll-china-landslide-rises-11-rescuers-still-search-missing-2024-01-23/</link><description>周二下午，中国云南省山体滑坡造成的死亡人数上升至20人，救援人员在严寒和大雪中奋力寻找数十名失踪人员。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 03:01:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/death-toll-china-landslide-rises-11-rescuers-still-search-missing-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国正在考虑2780亿美元的股市救助计划 - 彭博社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-weighs-stock-market-rescue-package-backed-by-278-bln-bloomberg-news-2024-01-23/</link><description>彭博新闻社周二援引知情人士的话报道称，中国当局正在考虑采取措施稳定暴跌的股市，此举引起了平淡投资者的质疑。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 02:53:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-weighs-stock-market-rescue-package-backed-by-278-bln-bloomberg-news-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>供应线索不一，油价稳定，中国前景谨慎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-slips-economic-concerns-eclipse-geopolitical-tensions-2024-01-23/</link><description>周二油价几乎没有变化，交易员权衡了一系列相互冲突的供需担忧，从中东紧张局势升级到寒冷天气扰乱美国生产。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 02:07:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-slips-economic-concerns-eclipse-geopolitical-tensions-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示韩国第四季度经济增速可能略有放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/south-koreas-economy-likely-grew-slightly-slower-pace-q4-2024-01-23/</link><description>路透社调查的经济学家表示，与第三季度相比，韩国经济在 2023 年最后三个月的扩张速度略有放缓，因为尽管出口增加，但利率上升抑制了内需。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 01:55:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/south-koreas-economy-likely-grew-slightly-slower-pace-q4-2024-01-23/</guid></item><item><title>全球股市回升，中国市场举步维艰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-23/</link><description>由于希望日本央行不会很快放弃其超级宽松政策，日本股市飙升。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 01:50:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>